  "description": "Traffic, latency, token usage, resilience (retries/circuit breakers) and cost-ledger health for synapse-gateway. All metrics are emitted via metrics-exporter-prometheus on the gateway's :9090 /metrics endpoint and scraped by the synapse-gateway ServiceMonitor.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "links": [],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "current": { "selected": true, "text": "synapse-gateway", "value": "synapse-gateway" },
        "hide": 0,
        "label": "Prometheus job",
        "name": "job",
        "options": [{ "selected": true, "text": "synapse-gateway", "value": "synapse-gateway" }],
        "query": "synapse-gateway",
        "skipUrlSync": false,
        "type": "textbox"
